title: 43 The Naked Wise Men
description:
"I have conquered the need to conquer the world" means "I have defeated the dark side of the Warrior Archetype within me." Is this possible? In today's episode we'll examine the true historical encounter in India between Alexander and the yogis of that era---called by the Macedonians gymnosophists--the "Naked Wise Men."

New episodes every Monday. SUBSCRIBE and REVIEW.
